 L:{em:'🧲🧲',t:'N meets S = ATTRACT',b:'Opposite poles pull together<br/>SNAP! 💥 They stick!'},R:{em:'🔄',t:'N meets N = REPEL',b:'Same poles push away<br/>😤 Cannot be forced together'},
 fun:'Earth is a giant magnet! Its iron core creates a magnetic field — that is why compasses work!',tip:'Opposite poles ATTRACT. Same poles REPEL. Magnetic = iron, steel, nickel, cobalt ONLY!'},
